{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"scale","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/scale","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n<p>属性<code>scale</code>定义了用在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feDisplacementMap\"><code>&lt;feDisplacementMap&gt;</code></a>滤镜上的置换缩放因子。它的总值表达在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a>元素的属性<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/primitiveUnits\">primitiveUnits</a></code>确定的坐标系统中。</p>\n<p>如果这个属性的值是<strong>0</strong>，则它的操作对源图像没有影响。</p>\n<p>如果没有指定这个属性，则效果等同于它被指定了<strong>0</strong>值。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>类别</th>\n      <th><em>无</em></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>值</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>可变性</td>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>scale</code>属性：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feDisplacementMap\"><code>&lt;feDisplacementMap&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[],"query":"svg.elements.feDisplacementMap.scale"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"scale","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"scale","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/scale","github_url":"https://gith